      "title": "Issuing of revenue licenses in NWP limited to 3 days a week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Vehicle revenue licences in the North-Western Province will be issued only on Mondays, Wednesdays and Thursdays from today. Licences expiring from 01 to 31 July will be extended until 31 August 2022."
      ],
